{"tid":2505320,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"喺Uniqlo被指使用新疆棉之際，香港分部公關竟然作出如此舉動！？","createTime":"2021-04-26T13:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T13:19:46.000Z","uid":219969,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b3cc7eeadd76884cba64291d75c3362201c90d86","tid":2505320,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo母公司：我哋政治中立，新疆人權問題唔答！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於中國新疆維吾爾族的人權問題時，迅銷董事長兼公司社長的柳井正回答：<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「在政治方面會抱持中立的立場。恕不評論。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z47Uk2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ47Uk2x.jpg&h=586f117c&s={SIZE}\" /> <a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210410/AE7EUAZYR5C2RDTIC6GWTIMS2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210410%2FAE7EUAZYR5C2RDTIC6GWTIMS2Q&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=4b70c2f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210410%2FAE7EUAZYR5C2RDTIC6GWTIMS2Q&h=830d194b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210410/AE7EUAZYR5C2RDTIC6GWTIMS2Q</a> <br />\n<br />\nUniqlo香港，都係「政治中立」，新聞審查問題唔答，假新聞問題唔答！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賺錢至上，繼續搵TVB藝人賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">🚫 Uniqlo 🚫</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/uniqlo.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funiqlo.hk&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=97cd11c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/uniqlo.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/nj4QxQXW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpili